name: only cutouts left.
description:
Dying vintage artifacts need to be saved. To save the glory of the vintage artifacts, I have made these posters. The name of the poster says that only cutouts left as in the future there will be no vintage things to admire. Only pictures cutouts and files will be left. I will be posting other posters like these with different themes to keep you guys inspired and creative.


see it on Behance :- https://www.behance.net/gallery/126663033/Only-cutouts-left
